high_descs: Walk to the sink then take a step to your right.
Pick up the towel that's on the ring on the wall in front of you.
Look down at the green garbage.
Put the towel in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a towel in the garbage.

high_descs: Walk forward and to the right to go to the hand towel holder.
Take the hand towel off the holder.
Look down at the trash can.
Put the towel in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the hand towel in the trash can.

high_descs: Go to the small space between the sink and the toilet, straight ahead of you.
Pull down the hand towel, hanging from the towel holder on the wall.
Step back from the wall so that you are in front of the green bin on the floor.
Place the towel in the green bin on the floor, between the sink and toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a towel in the green bin.
